cloud your judgment.

38
00:04:26,300 --> 00:04:27,220
Alright.

39
00:04:27,310 --> 00:04:28,170
Don't be upset.

40
00:04:29,070 --> 00:04:30,360
No matter what you decide,

41
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:31,420
