218
00:14:17,580 --> 00:14:18,540
Emergency case.

219
00:14:18,580 --> 00:14:21,310
You need acupuncture now. Your life is in danger.

220
00:14:21,480 --> 00:14:21,870
Where are my needles?

221
00:14:21,870 --> 00:14:24,120
Suye is the worst.

222
00:14:24,120 --> 00:14:26,050
